CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 24, 1959, pg. 19, reads: "Seton Hill Bash - Walt Harper, who has been doing many of the college dances and concerts, was featured last week at a jazz concert and dance for Seton Hill College at the Jackson Hotel. Next week the Harper crew invades the Crawford Grill, and then they play proms at California State Teachers and W. and J. Colleges. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Walt Harper playing piano, people seated at banquet tables, for jazz concert and dance at the Jackson Hotel for Seton Hill College, another version
